GRTrackingVendorInfo.name: GRTrackingVendorInfo
GRTrackingVendorInfo.queryString:
SELECT
    DISTINCT
	a.ab_coorsa as vendor_code,
	RTRIM(a.ab_tle) + ' ' + RTRIM(a.ab_naor) as vendor_name,
	a.ab_ofss as address,
	a.ab_tne as telephone,
	a.ab_emss as email,
	b.ab_name as name
FROM
	tl_ms_ve a
	JOIN tl_ms_em b ON a.ab_coorsa = b.ab_coorsa
WHERE
	a.ab_coorsa = :vendorcode
GRTrackingVendorInfo.countQueryString:
select count(*) from (SELECT
    DISTINCT
	a.ab_coorsa as vendor_code,
	RTRIM(a.ab_tle) + ' ' + RTRIM(a.ab_naor) as vendor_name,
	a.ab_ofss as address,
	a.ab_tne as telephone,
	a.ab_emss as email,
	b.ab_name as name
FROM
	tl_ms_ve a
	JOIN tl_ms_em b ON a.ab_coorsa = b.ab_coorsa
WHERE
	a.ab_coorsa = :vendorcode) wmTempTable
